name: Ancient Roman Coin Pendant
description:
I love ancient coins, particularly the coins that circulated in the marketplace and are somewhat worn from use. I feel that these coins connect us directly to the past and remind of us of what we have in common not only with our ancestors but what we have in common with People of all nations around the world.

This coin was set in a Silver Bezel and is hung on an 18" chain.

CUSTOM MADE TO ORDER. 

CUSTOM ORDER: Each piece takes approximately 3-4 weeks to hand make and ship.
